===后期发展===
2021年12月3日，官方透露，现年62岁的马士沙拉末依旧被无限期监禁，他依旧不肯放弃他的极端思想。他的长子马西哈迪（Masyhadi）也同样加入了伊斯兰祈祷团，并且在2013年被逮捕并无限期关押至今。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.todayonline.com/singapore/ji-arrests-20-years-4-members-still-detained-under-internal-security-act-including-mas|title=JI arrests, 20 years on: 4 members still detained under Internal Security Act, including Mas Selamat and son|date=3 December 2021|website=Today|language=en|access-date=9 December 2021|archive-date=2021-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211209145425/https://www.todayonline.com/singapore/ji-arrests-20-years-4-members-still-detained-under-internal-security-act-including-mas|dead-url=no}}</ref>

